                            </entry>
                            <entry colspan="2" spanname="SPAN2">
                                <para>If voltage is >0.039V, check ground circuit for resistance >5&#x2126;. Measure
                                    resistance between PIN A and PIN 19 (spec &#60; 5&#x2126;) using a breakout box to
